# 🌐 Small Office Network using Cisco Packet Tracer

## 📖 Project Overview

This project demonstrates the design and implementation of a Small Office Network using Cisco Packet Tracer.

The network consists of two departments (HR and Sales) connected through routers and switches. DHCP is used for automatic IP address allocation, and routing enables communication between different networks.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Design a small office network
- Configure routers and switches
- Configure DHCP
- Enable communication between departments
- Verify network connectivity

